```python id="f9v2p5"
[1,0,2,0]
```

---

# Final Understanding

This solution:

1. Takes each number
2. Converts it into digits
3. Appends digits one-by-one
4. Returns the final flattened digit array

Simple and clean approach using:

```text id="d5m7x9"
String Conversion + Nested Loop
```
